<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900702-0154</DOCNO><DOCID>900702-0154.</DOCID><HL>   Control Resource Buy-Back</HL><DATE>07/02/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C14</SO><CO>   CRIX</CO><IN>BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)</IN><LP>   MICHIGAN CITY, Ind. -- Control Resource Industries Inc.,which makes equipment and supplies used in asbestos abatementand industrial safety products, said its board authorized thepurchase of an additional 500,000 common shares under itsJuly 1988 program that initially allowed buying back as manyas 200,000 shares. The company has about 5.4 million sharesoutstanding.   Shares bought back will be used for general corporatepurposes, Control Resource said.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>